Taybar Rozziss was a drow fighter and mage inhabiting the city of Zhentil Keep during the lateâ€“14 century DR.
Taybar served under Kebella Mizzrym of House Mizzrym in secrecy within Sunset House within southern Zhentil Keep in the eastern section of the Foreign Quarter. He was Kebellas consort.
